FBIS4-4917 "dreas066_c_94038" FBIS-EAS-94-066 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 North Korea Works of President Kim Il-song Reported Abroad Works of President Kim Il-song Reported Abroad SK0104110194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1009 GMT 1 Apr 94 SK0104110194 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 1 (KCNA) -- The Indian paper INDIAN TIMES carried the full text of "For the Ultimate Solution of the Rural Question Under the Banner of the Socialist Rural Theses", a letter sent by the great leader President Kim Il-song to a national agricultural conference. Detailed gists of the letter were carried by the Cameroonian paper LA VISION and the Bulgarian paper TRIBUNA. The Togolese paper ATOPANI and the Zairean paper LE STANDARD carried articles explaining his work "10-point Programme of the Great Unity of the Whole Nation for the Reunification of the Country".
